{"tid":708553,"cid":14,"subCid":0,"title":"論返工時間痾屎","createTime":"2018-06-19T11:39:06.000Z","updateTime":"2018-06-21T14:23:55.000Z","uid":65598,"like":86,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":18,"replies":[{"pid":"53bc196bc6b23585782bf9f2b836880037de0095","tid":708553,"uid":65598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T11:39:06.000Z","msg":"除左有D人認廁所之外, 其實返緊工痾屎真係好爽<br />\n每日入去坐返15,20分鐘, 真係一絕:<br />\n<br />\n1. 拎部電話上網又好, 連登又好, 好過用公司電腦上唔覺意睇到丁圖 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/banghead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n2. 打鋪機又得, 平時唔係唔打得, 但果個moment唔會有人無啦啦叫你先 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n3. 養成定時痾屎習慣, 真既, 痾開真係差不多日日果段時間去痾 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n4. 用返公時間去痾, 即係用緊公司錢去痾屎喎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/tongue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  唔係用緊你夜晚私人時間去痾, <br />\n    慳返5-15分鐘, 唔計有D人便祕要坐半粒鐘 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n5. 做左咁耐野, 入去靜下, 大條道理入去鬆一鬆<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/good.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n總之就係正<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/touch.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n唔信聽日試下,包你上癮 <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/wet.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"44abede406cc00efda67e8ff7f95de11380e2300","tid":708553,"uid":65598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T11:44:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c10f3dc287a8eff16f5ef6ec67c74e6a17d130aa","tid":708553,"uid":73567,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T11:46:36.000Z","msg":"入去禁陣電話又得<br />\n入去訓陣覺又得<br />\n屙屎果20分鐘就好似獲得自由咁<br />\n最緊要係公司比錢你屙屎<br />\n真係要屙爆個馬桶佢都要屙!"},{"pid":"806d7b51dc546b4acac26c6dd49e1fe961d0d3e7","tid":708553,"uid":2547,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":3,"replyTime":"2018-06-19T11:49:46.000Z","msg":"公區廁所收唔到data<img src=\"/assets/faces/norm